{"tid":2504842,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"視點31  昇哥對紅底強","createTime":"2021-04-26T07:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T12:33:43.000Z","uid":30,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b2bfac995fa90119344dad48b4f0bd41692e7a2","tid":2504842,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"【LIVE預告！】<br />\n<br />\n甚麼是「假新聞」？<br />\n香港又有冇「假新聞」？<br />\n如果有，出自何處？<br />\n<br />\n最近，警務處處長鄧炳強多次提到「假新聞」問題，表示若有法例針對「假新聞」將會是好事。<br />\n<br />\n不過，若立法規管，如何定義「假新聞」？如何在防止錯誤訊息流傳的同時，又否確保規管不會變成打壓傳媒的武器？<br />\n<br />\n聽晚8點，我地請黎工聯會立法會議員郭偉強、以及記協副主席兼《立場新聞》副採訪主任陳朗昇，<br />\n港台電視31、facebook專頁同步直播！"},{"pid":"dbe4e77e28515c139be9aa79260baaa13c268adf","tid":2504842,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"22605370471f002593072b3df1e0ada149c649b5","tid":2504842,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"到時就會清算19年到依家啲記者媒體"},{"pid":"6602ab0402154624864e206fa552c958a2a215da","tid":2504842,"uid":86449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:43:24.000Z","msg":"Pk tang 呢排好勤力上鏡<br />\n做埋777 果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c570f8654aa85f408bfd04a37cc651e46ea8766","tid":2504842,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T08:06:25.000Z","msg":"哩單咪警方FB發假新聞囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%86%AB%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E6%8F%AD%E6%9B%BE%E6%B4%BE%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A5%E7%94%A2%E6%88%BF-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-fb-%E5%B8%96%E6%96%87%E5%88%AA-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%AA%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%94%A2%E6%88%BF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596